Review.create({ title: "THIS NEW NOVEL WILL HAVE NO PROBLEM SELLING", rating: 4, body: "This collaboration between award winning James Patterson and author David Ellis has produced interesting results. If you like the murder/mystery genre you won't be disappointed with this new novel. The characters are well designed, dialog is witty & appropriate and the plot, while occasionally borderline &#34;spooky,&#34; works very well at holding the suspense and a readers interest. The collaboration seems to have brought some new original texture into Patterson's successful writing style, adding a breath of fresh air. Well done.", user_id: user8.id, book_id: book38.id })
