Review.create({ title: "A definite winner!", rating: 5, body: "This book was so suspenseful that I actually tore off a couple of fingernails. One of the best stand alone books so far! I did not guess the ending. I also didn't get much housework done because I could not put the book down. Excellent writing style, good character development and fats paced just the way I like my books to be. The one complaint is that the price for an e-book of $15 is ridiculously high!!! I see no reason for that except greed on the part of somebody. I still gave it 5 stars although I wanted to drop it down to 4 stars for the overcharging. But the book was excellent!", user_id: user10.id, book_id: book38.id })
