Review.create({ title: "This boxed set is a must have!!!!", rating: 5, body: "This wonderfully inspirational story has helped my middle school students to remember that, as people, we all struggle with many things in our lives and are very blessed by the friends and families who love and support us in our lives.  We continue to revisit the story as we think about and discuss the daily precepts from the second book.  This is a must have book set in every household, counseling or therapist's office and every classroom.", user_id: user5.id, book_id: book44.id })
