Review.create({ title: "Fun ride...", rating: 5, body: "Hayden and Penny's fake marriage turned into real love story is a fun ride! He's a billionaire and needs a wife.... She's a normal girl who just got from Cuba and needs a baby ASAP. They strike a deal and VIOLA! You are enjoying their ride to a HEA.I couldn't put it done and was sad to see it end. Nicole Snow does a great job weaving multiple issues and then wraps them up nicely... with a beautiful bow. Although Maybe Hayden should have had to grovel a bit more... but who am I to fight the script.Can't wait for the next read!", user_id: user3.id, book_id: book97.id })
Review.create({ title: "Love Conquers All &lt;3 &lt;3 &lt;3", rating: 5, body: "What a GREAT story!  I love Nicole Snow's writing style.  This story has it all - sex, lies and fairy tales!  Hot sex too, and lots of it!!!!Hayden, Billionaire, battling a crazy money grubbing step-mom that wants what's rightfully his and his brothers'; and he's a Playboy that dipped into a bat shit psycho for a brief period and moved on.  Penny, a virgin that took a once in a lifetime trip and came back with the Zeno virus from a mosquito bite that will take away her ability to have children within the next 18 months.  There is a loophole in Hayden's fathers will that will allow him to keep the family business and riches.  A deal is struck between Hayden & Penny...he gets what he needs and she gets a baby and they both walk away with what they want.  BUT - that's not how life is ;)  Love happens!!  Well, then jealous psycho exes, money chasing step-mothers, eves dropping employees, and the Media that soaks it all up and spews the garbage they're fed without worrying about fallout or truth.  It ends with a beautiful HEA and everyone gets what they deserve!  There's more, but you gotta read it!  It is WELL WORTH IT!!!  I Loved this story and pretty much anything written by Nicole Snow!", user_id: user4.id, book_id: book97.id })
Review.create({ title: "a refreshingly phenomenal romantic suspense that will sizzle and burn as it seduces and intoxicates all of your senses", rating: 5, body: "Baby Fever Bride is a refreshingly phenomenal romantic suspense that will sizzle and burn as it seduces and intoxicates all of your senses. There is never a dull moment, and you will find brilliant twists and turns that will make your head spin and your heart race. This is an absolutely perfect storm that drives home real life issues while not forgetting about the soul deep love and lethal danger that is always right around the corner. There is nothing better than a story that stimulates my over-worked mind and throws my heart in a beautiful tizzy!Penny&#8217;s life has suddenly been thrust into utter chaos and turmoil. She has just been handed a life-altering sentence, and she doesn&#8217;t know how to face or even begin to fight it. No matter what she knows something has got to give. Hayden finds himself plunged into the impossible. He does not understand how it suddenly came to this, but he isn&#8217;t going down without a fight. He will win or he will take everyone down with him. When Fate drives these two together we discover that something explosive is in works. Beyond anything rational, they know there is something strong and sure between them that neither can explain. Their two worlds will collide with the force of an atomic bomb, and no one is safe from the fallout. Will they allow others to tear their delicate future to shreds before it even begins, or will they fight tooth and nail for what they truly want?Oh how I loved Hayden&#8217;s intensity and focus for what he wants, and Penny had my heart breaking for the burden she is given to bear. These are two extraordinary and incredible characters that captured my heart and refused to give it back. I fell in love with them both so hard that is literally hurt. There is no middle ground with these two.Read more &rsaquo;", user_id: user5.id, book_id: book97.id })
