Review.create({ title: "I love a sexy hockey player!", rating: 5, body: "Loved this! Nothing better than a hot hockey player! In the beginning, Alex comes across as a huge jerk who has earned his MVP title - Most Valuable Prick. Honestly, I couldn't stand him at first and really thought there was no way I was going to be able to like him. He isn't nice to his teammates, he isn't nice to his fans and he doesn't do relationships. Then, when you start learning about his past, you really get an idea of what made him the way he was. I loved Sutton and how her relationship with Alex developed. She was strong, beautiful and sweet. I loved that Sutton also didn't have the best past but she didn't let it change her and she used her hurt to help others. She was really an amazing character. This book was really steamy. I loved Garrett and hope that his book is next in the series. I really enjoyed this book and can't wait to read more in this series.", user_id: user2.id, book_id: book154.id })
