Review.create({ title: "Not to be missed...another home run by Kerry Lonsdale", rating: 5, body: "When I find an author who has a debut that knocks it out of the park, like Kerry did with Everything We Keep, I can't wait to read their next novel. It can go one of two ways, right? Well friends, Kerry Lonsdale knocks it out of the park, again with All the Breaking Waves!I had to digest the book for a few hours before sitting down and writing this review, to try and capture in just a few words what I think about this novel. (I don't like reading long reviews, so I tend not to write them).Riveting, Heartfelt, Emotional, Suspenseful, Heartbreaking, and Loving. All adjectives I would use to describe the story about Molly, her daughter Cassie, Molly's Nana, and throw in Molly's old flame - Owen. I absolutely could not put this book down, I was immediately drawn into their story and had to know what happened next, immediately!This is a novel about love first, and what you won't do to keep those around you safe and protected.I received an ARC of All the Breaking Waves in exchange for an honest review, and honestly - I have another book hangover. What's the cure for that? Kerry's third book - not due out until next year!", user_id: user8.id, book_id: book159.id })
