Review.create({ title: "So good!", rating: 5, body: "Wow! What an incredible book! When I read Kerry Lonsdale's debut novel, Everything We Keep, I was immediately hooked on her writing style. So, when I heard that she had another book coming out I knew that I needed to get it! I was not disappointed!Molly has special powers that were passed on through her mother and grandmother. Now, her daughter, Cassy, has the same powers. In an attempt to protect her daughter and learn to harness these abilities, Molly returns home to her Nana. She reunites with friends and her first love who offer her all of their support. Molly finds that sometimes the things that you think you should shut out are the things that you should embrace.I don't want to go into more detail to give any of the story away. All I can say is buy it and read it! I devoured this book! You will love it!", user_id: user12.id, book_id: book159.id })
