book160 = Book.create({ title: "Sold: Highest Bidder", author: "Lauren Landish", image_url: "https://res.cloudinary.com/dt72mzjpx/image/upload/book_160.jpg", publisher: "", date: "", description: " She&#x2019;s scared and broken, but soon she&#x2019;ll be mine.I was only a boy when I saw my mother murdered in front of me. That does something to a man. It turns him hard, cold and makes him an addict for control.  In all things.My desires are dark and what I&#x2019;m interested in is far more than simple submission.  I&#x2019;ve been waiting for someone as broken as me.  Someone who truly needs to give up complete control and rely on me to take away her pain. And then I found her. Katia.  My kitten. The moment I laid eyes on her gorgeous face, full lips and seductive curves, she stole the air from my lungs. It&#x2019;s been so long since I&#x2019;ve wanted something so intensely.  She devours my every waking moment, teasing me with just a taste.  She&#x2019;s stronger than she knows, but haunted by a past that won&#x2019;t loosen its grip on her.  She&#x2019;s refused my collar and I know why. The last one she wore wasn&#x2019;t by choice.  But this time she&#x2019;s going to beg for it.I can give her what he didn&#x2019;t -  true domination and trust. I&#x2019;ll own her pleasure, her happiness and she can sate my desire for complete control.  I only need her to give me a chance.Just one chance to buy her.  The moment she agrees and steps on that stage at the auction, she&#x2019;s mine. But she doesn&#x2019;t have to worry, I&#x2019;ll care for all her desires.*Sold is a full-length standalone DARK romance with an HEA, no cheating, and no cliffhanger.", amazon_link: "https://www.amazon.com/Sold-Highest-Bidder-Willow-Winters-ebook/dp/B01N5JUGTU", kobo_link: "https://www.kobo.com/us/en/search?query=Sold:%20Highest%20Bidder%20Lauren%20Landish", play_link: "https://play.google.com/store/search?c=books&hl=en&q=Sold:%20Highest%20Bidder%20Lauren%20Landish" })
Review.create({ title: "Intense, dark yet beautiful", rating: 5, body: "Willow Winters and Lauren Landish are amazing co-writers and have done it again. This series just keeps getting better and more gritty. We are back at Club X for Issac and Katia's incredibly intense and emotional story. Both are trying to deal with the past... and what broken and horrible pasts they've had to endure. Katia was kidnapped and held as a slave for four years, while Issac witnessed his mothers murder. They are both deeply wounded souls who have a very unconventional way of finding healing in each other.Both are understandably damaged and scarred but they are both strong and are coming over the other side of their pain. Even though the book does deal with some dark areas the authors don't go into explicit detail on Katia's past... the book is more about healing - which what makes it so beautiful in my opinion.We met Isaac in the previous book &#34;Bought&#34;, but that glimpse of him didn't even prepare the reader for the man we see in this book.This story was very dark and heart wrenching at times, but you just can't put it down or give up on the characters - there were parts that had me just shocked and devastated, but these great authors take us on an excellent journey and the ending is worth the roller-coaster ride. Absolutely fantastic read for me - it truly is dark but stunning in its beauty.It's not necessary to read the first story, Bought to understand Sold as it works as a standalone, but I highly recommend that as well. This book ends at 39% and there are two bonus books also worth reading -Inked and Bad Boys.(I am a verified purchaser in Australia)", user_id: user1.id, book_id: book160.id })
