Review.create({ title: "Not as dark as you might think", rating: 5, body: "Terrible things have been done to Katia after her abduction. Things we can't even imagine. But she has endured. She has escaped. She has survived. Now she needs to heal. Isaac knows what she needs. He knows from the darkness within himself. When he sees Katia at the club, he knows immediately that she is his. What he fights against is being hers. He feels tainted by what he has done in his past. He feels unworthy of her -- of her submission and of her love. Although that's exactly what he thirsts for. While their path is strewn with missteps, they find their way. It's hot. It's humbling. It's healing. For both of them.", user_id: user3.id, book_id: book160.id })
