Review.create({ title: "Wow! Just Wow!!!", rating: 5, body: "I am amazed that these 2 authors, Willow Winters & Lauren Landish, were able to outdo Bought: Highest Bidder, which was an amazingly sexy& touching story...and they did! Isaac was a broken man feeling guilt for doing nothing while his mother was being murdered. Katia was kidnapped at 16 y.o. and sold as a sex slave and abused beyond imagination for 4 years. Katia was withdrawn and unable to socialize due to her past. Isaac, unable to love due to his abusive past. Together, they explore, flourish and love...and it's sexy, romantic, amazing! It is emotionally addictive!  Once I started this book, I literally could not put it down! Do Not pass this one up!!!", user_id: user5.id, book_id: book160.id })
