Review.create({ title: "Loved this addition to the Highest Bidder series", rating: 5, body: "I loved this story.  Even though I was gifted a review copy by the authors, I had to purchase it (you have to support your favorite authors to keep them writing).  Katia and Isaac are both tortured by events in their past.  I think the authors did a good job of bringing Katia's torments and coping to the pages of this book.  I loved the twist with Katia's on-line friend.  Even though the book deals with some dark subjects, the authors don't go into explicit detail on Katia's past.  The book is more about healing.  Madam Lynn does her best to help these two characters and I really hope that Madam Lynn gets her own story.  I can't wait for the next in the series (Joe is going to find his match).  Give this series a read and you won't regret it.  At the moment this book includes a copy of Inked and Bad Boy (both were also very good reads).", user_id: user8.id, book_id: book160.id })
