Review.create({ title: "THE SAVIOR IS SAVED !", rating: 5, body: "I voluntarily reviewed an Advanced Reader Copy of this book.Isaac is the head of security for Club X. He's into the BDSM lifestyle, but more Master/slave relationships. It's what he needs. He has yet to find his perfect slave.Katia owns a doggy daycare/shelter. Katia suffers from debilitating night terrors regarding her past. While Isaac uses his business to deal with his past, Katia uses hers to cope. Katia receives an invitation to Club X and that's where she meets Isaac. Their first encounter is amazing, but it doesn't end as Isaac planned. Katia is afraid, and with her past, she has reason to be. Isaac wants to be her everything. He needs to convince her that he is the Master that she needs. Katia needs to put her painful past to rest and let Isaac take care of her. Isaac realizes he could never keep Katia; she's too good for him, but he can help her heal. Isaac wants to save her from her past, but who will save him?Isaac is a genuinely good man. He wants to do right by Katia. He's led a hard life and that's what made him who he is today. Katia is just trying to get by, from one day to the next. She needs what Isaac can give her, but she fears that by giving up complete control, it might lead to Isaac becoming her jailer. They are so much better together. Isaac was patient and willing to do whatever it took to heal Katia.Based on the the blurb, I thought I had a good idea about what this book was about. Wrong. It was so much better. The storyline, the characters and the way it was told.I KNEW ISAAC AND KATIA'S BOOK WAS GOING TO BE AWESOME AND I WAS NOT DISAPPOINTED !I ABSOLUTELY LOVED THIS BOOK !  AMAZING STORY, WELL WRITTEN, VERY GRIPPING AND EMOTIONAL !  HEART WRENCHING !  THEIR CHEMISTRY WAS OFF THE CHARTS !  THE SEX WAS SIZZLING, EDGY, PURE UNADULTERATED PASSION !  VERY HOT !DEFINITELY ONE-CLICK THIS ASAP ! ! !", user_id: user12.id, book_id: book160.id })
