book198 = Book.create({ title: "Lip Service (A Pleasure Chest Story)", author: "Penny Wylder", image_url: "https://res.cloudinary.com/dt72mzjpx/image/upload/book_198.jpg", publisher: "", date: "", description: " I never imagined I&#x2019;d be taking a class on how to perform better in bed.But when my rude ex told me I sucked at, well, sucking, I couldn&#x2019;t stop thinking about how awful that made me feel.Then I saw the hot guy teaching my class&#x2026;and I stopped thinking entirely.Philip Crew is six and a half feet of pure, sizzling muscle and panty-dropping sexual tension. And he definitely has no problem instructing me on what he likes.There are tons of women drooling over him, so why does he keep flirting with me? The attention is addictive. But I just got out of a relationship with a player, and Philip is giving me the same vibes.When he offers to teach me in private, I know things are going too far.The last thing I want is to get hurt again.Except I can&#x2019;t get him out of my head. I want to try out everything he taught me&#x2026; on him.My only hope of keeping myself from unzipping his jeans and seeing what&#x2019;s beneath is to stay away. If I never see him again, I know I can resist.Then he bumps into me right outside my apartment.And I forget why I was fighting my desire in the first place.This is a standalone novella with a HEA and NO cheating!Penny Wylder writes just that-- wild romances. Happily Ever Afters are always better when they're a little dirty, so if you're looking for a page turner that will make you feel naughty in all the right places, jump right in and leave your panties at the door!", amazon_link: "https://www.amazon.com/Lip-Service-Pleasure-Chest-Story-ebook/dp/B01N9SH38D", kobo_link: "https://www.kobo.com/us/en/search?query=Lip%20Service%20(A%20Pleasure%20Chest%20Story)%20Penny%20Wylder", play_link: "https://play.google.com/store/search?c=books&hl=en&q=Lip%20Service%20(A%20Pleasure%20Chest%20Story)%20Penny%20Wylder" })
Review.create({ title: "The characters are wonderful with out of this world chemistry", rating: 5, body: "I voluntarily reviewed an advanced readers copy of this book for the author.  As always Penny Wylder blows us away with another hot as hell story. I can never get enough of her work. This book was hot and steamy in all the right places. The characters are wonderful with out of this world chemistry.  This is an absolute must read you won't want to miss out on.", user_id: user1.id, book_id: book198.id })
Review.create({ title: "Most Instructional!!!", rating: 5, body: "I swear my kindle was melting in my hands this read was so incredibly, wonderfully, beautifully hot and yummy!!! Every lady can use a refresher course in giving the one you love Lip Service... And did we ever get one in the framework of a challenging love story.  Mayra thought she was utterly lacking in bedroom skills goes to classes to try to improve and she meets the teacher, Ive ever encountered someone who embodied the essence of man, the testosterone is practically rolling off him in waves. His face has a wildness about it, like its spent more time in nature than the rest of us and wasnt able to be tamed. He looks fierce and rugged and something deep down inside me shivers. - MayraSuch masterful descriptive writing skill and emotionally engrossing prose written by Ms. Wylder!Mayra. The thought of her clears up the darkness lurking in my head. Its like seeing a sliver of blue sky on a cloudy day. Just a glimpse of hope a reminder that things arent necessarily as bleak as you think they are. - PhilipThe characters in this love story have their complexities and some issues that keep this shorter storyline engaging.For a hot, hot, hot enjoyable and...ahem...instructional interlude in your day, this is your one-click to happiness, romance lovers.I was so grateful to have the opportunity to read an ARC, however, the final copy just had to be a purchase for my kindle library.  My reading and reviewing was completely voluntarily. One did not influence the other. My thoughts are my own and they come from my head, heart and in this case maybe even other places !", user_id: user2.id, book_id: book198.id })
Review.create({ title: "Lip Service", rating: 5, body: "Penny Wylder has done it again. Her writing is outstanding. I don't normally buy books, I either read through KU or get the free ones on Amazon and iBooks but first, when I saw it was by Penny and then, when I read the blurb, I knew I had to read this book. And, I was NOT disappointed at all.Mayra's sleazy ex-boyfriend told her she was horrible at sex and that the rest of her didn't make up for it so she decided to take a sex class called, blowjobs and beyond, hoping to improve before her next relationship. The regular instructor was out sick so her friend, Phillip was filling in. Mayra thought Phillip was hot at first sight and he liked what he saw in her as well. During and after class they flirted with each other but Mayra got scared and ran away. Thinking they would never see each other again, they both spent the night fantasizing about one another. As luck would have it they literally ran into each other the next day. Given a second chance, would they use it or throw it away? Would Mayra allow her hang ups about her sexual expertise keep her from being with Phillip?", user_id: user3.id, book_id: book198.id })
book199 = Book.create({ title: "Lip Service", author: "Simone Sowood", image_url: "https://res.cloudinary.com/dt72mzjpx/image/upload/book_199.jpg", publisher: "", date: "", description: " My new neighbor is an online s*x advice vlogger -- but she doesn&apos;t know that I knowOut of curiosity, I checked out her videos. Who wouldn&apos;t?I didn&apos;t count on being tempted by her silky voice or her full lips.Too bad she&apos;s off limits.Being a single dad isn&apos;t easy, and I have rules -- no relationships, and no screwing close to home.But when I become the subject of her posts, I can&apos;t keep my hands off her any longer.I have to teach her everything she got wrong in her videos.*** A steamy STANDALONE full length contemporary romance novel with a hot, dominant bad boy alpha. No cliffhanger, no cheating, and a guaranteed happily-ever-after.***", amazon_link: "https://www.amazon.com/Lip-Service-Simone-Sowood-ebook/dp/B01N9O0DNN", kobo_link: "https://www.kobo.com/us/en/search?query=Lip%20Service%20Simone%20Sowood", play_link: "https://play.google.com/store/search?c=books&hl=en&q=Lip%20Service%20Simone%20Sowood" })
Review.create({ title: "Okay with a few good laughs", rating: 3, body: "Lip Service by Simone SowoodAvery is a vlogger on You Tube.  She promotes sex items and advice on relationships and sex.  She has numerous followers.  However she has been single for six months after a break up from a long term relationship.  She moves to a small town and lands up living next door to the not so friendly, Knox.  Knox knows who she is, but Avery does not realize that until he plays her.  Knox is a single Dad and has put restriction is place that he will never date or introduce his daughter to any women who he has a sexual relationship with.  He basically uses women for his relief, no strings attached. When Piper, his daughter makes friends with Avery, things change.  Know and Avery start to interact and decide to get together for a sexual relationship while keeping this hidden from Piper.  There are some real amusing situations that develop.  The plot was interesting.  I did not really feel the chemistry between the main characters.  Dont get me wrong, the sex was enticing but there was just something missing.  Overall it was good and I enjoyed the storyReviewed for Hot Books and Sassy Girls Book Blog", user_id: user1.id, book_id: book199.id })
Review.create({ title: "A hilarious, wonderful love story", rating: 5, body: "What to say about Lip Service? Think it all depends on your sense of humor. All I can say is that it hit me just the right place and I was rolling around the floor while reading this book. I found it absolutely hilarious.First of all, I have never thought about being a Vlogger and what that all means. Yeah, I have seen videos on YouTube and seen bedrooms and rooms in the background, but I have never thought more about it. Until now!Avery is a vlogger. She is giving sex advice to both men and women, and she is really successful. The problem is that she has been single for the past six months and her ex-boyfriend was not her roots to inspiration. Thats why she is running out of material to vlog about, in a slow but steady pace. She has earned enough money by vlogging to buy a house in a small town, and she has just moved in.Knox is living next door to Avery. He is a single dad to a thirteen-year-old daughter, and he has never been in a relationship, because of her. He wants to give her a steady upbringing, and therefore its just the two of them. Piper, his daughter, and Avery becomes friends really fast, and this is when Avery and Knoxs fight not to give in to the attraction between them, begins.Mrs. Sowood has really nailed it or is it me she has nailed (?) this time. I found her characters funny and sweet and I could have read much more of them. Knox is a really cocky bastard, but I would have to admit that he was swoon worthy.The chemistry between Avery and Knox was delicious, and the sex scenes were sizzling hot.I hope Simone Sowood continues to write with this humor, because I have not had enough of that, for sure.Thanks to Simone Sowood for this hilarious advanced copy.PS. If anyone is wondering. I loved this book so much that I just had to have a real copy of it.", user_id: user2.id, book_id: book199.id })
Review.create({ title: "Need Revving? Try out Knox!!!", rating: 5, body: "I found this story through a newsletter. After reading the book description, I was hooked. This story will definitely rev the imagination of the reader. This is the first book I've read from this author, and after reading this one, I will be reading more from her.I loved how her writing brought out the essence of this story. Feelings and emotions were heartfelt, along with some hot, sexy scenes that had me panting. I think I've found a book boyfriend. The characters were compelling with realistic flaws and desires. Even the responsibility of parenting was a great asset throughout the story. The pace was steady and the plot was believeable with some humorous moments.Avery and Knox are neighbors. Both have responsibilities, needs and desires that are very important to them. Situations will draw them together with passion. Will they endure being lonely because of their responsibilities?I recommend this book to all readers who finding a book boyfriend that's hot and responsible. Get the book, read it, and you can decide.I chose to review this story on my own.Happy Reading!!", user_id: user3.id, book_id: book199.id })
